      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TICKETS (6) goes very well here starting 10 times for four wins and two minors. Hit the frame latest (16.91) when third at Healesville in a Grade 5 H. Looks a key chance on best form. ZORRO DEVERE (5) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 5th and beaten only 3.5 lengths (30.05) at Sandown. Should be in this for a long way. BUN QUAKE (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (30.55) in a Grade 4/5 at The Meadows. Has a good record at this journey. One of the better hopes. AFFORDABILITY (2) can measure up with the right run.",
